akas: Dwayne "The Rock "Johnson YouTube Channel USA (informal title)
akas from release info: Dwayne "The Rock "Johnson YouTube Channel USA (informal title)

-1.title: What the Rock is Cooking: GIANT Red Velvet Whoopie Pie for Valentine's Day
-1.plot: The Rock wants you to cook up the ultimate Valentine's Day dessert for the special one in your life. Check out the video's description to find out how to make a GIANT Chocolate Chip Red Velvet Whoopie Pie.

1.title: The Rock Presents: Ascendance - Official Trailer
1.plot: In this high-brow action movie trailer, a young woman treks through the brush to discover the greatest secret of our time. Attain ASCENDANCE with Dwayne Johnson AKA The Rock on YouTube this July 18th.

2.title: The YouTube Factory Feat. Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson, Lilly Singh, and More!
2.plot: As Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson begins his YouTube career, his good friend Lilly Singh AKA iisuperwomanii gives him a tour around the remote volcanic island where all of your favorite videos get made.

3.title: Rock the Promo - Meet the Contestants! (S1 E0)
3.plot: "Rock the Promo" is a contest in which 32 finalists (chosen from thousands of contestants) will go head-to-head in a single-elimination bracket to determine who has the biggest, baddest, and funniest wrestling persona.

4.title: Pokemon Go: New Rock Pokemon?
4.plot: Pokemon Go is a worldwide phenomenon and trainers across the globe are in search of the rarest monsters. MatPat and Ali-A are here to show you the latest rare Pokemon that can be found in the wild. Featuring the singer of the original Pokemon Theme, Jason Paige.

5.title: Rock the Promo - Hosted by Joe Santagato, Feat. Kurt Angle (S1 E1)
5.plot: Joe Santagato and wrestling superstar Kurt Angle have teamed up with The Rock to bring you the first episode of "Rock The Promo". This week, they'll judge the first 8 contestants on their humor, intensity, and toughness to see who truly knows how to rock a promo.

6.title: The Rock Thank You for One Million Subscribers!
6.plot: It's been a FAST and FURIOUS (heh) ride ever since the The Rock's channel launched a little over a month ago, but thanks to viewers like you we've hit the million subscriber mark.

7.title: MATAFIED: The Style of Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson with Robert Mata (E1)
7.plot: Robert Mata, Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson's longtime stylist, gives you the inside scoop on how he creates styles for The Rock's red carpet events and his character Spencer Strasmore on HBO's "Ballers".

8.title: POKEROCK THEME Feat. Original Pokemon Singer JASON PAIGE (Official Lyric Video)
8.plot: PokeRock is back - and this time with the official lyric video for the PokeRock Theme Song featuring Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and the singer of the original Pokemon Theme, Jason Paige.

9.title: Rock the Promo - Hosted by Joe Santagato, Feat. Vickie Guerrero (S1 E2)
9.plot: Joe Santagato and pro wrestling's #1 bad girl Vickie Guerrero have teamed up with The Rock to bring you the second episode of "Rock The Promo". This week, they'll judge the bottom left bracket of contestants on their humor, intensity, and toughness to see who truly knows how to rock a promo.

10.title: PokeRock Returns to Pokemon Go - Feat. Seth Rogen
10.plot: Now that PokeRock is out in the wild and trainers across the world are attempting to be the very best (like no one ever was), a new trainer has appeared to try his hand at capturing the mythical Pokemon - Seth Rogen.

11.title: Rock the Promo - Hosted by Joe Santagato, Feat. Rey Mysterio (S1 E3)
11.plot: Joe Santagato and the greatest luchador of all time, pro wrestler Rey Mysterio, have teamed up with The Rock to bring you the third episode of "Rock The Promo". This week, they'll judge the top right bracket of contestants on their humor, intensity, and toughness to see who truly knows how to rock a promo.

12.title: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and Kevin Hart Visit Snapchat HQ!
12.plot: While out promoting the hit film "Central Intelligence", Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and Kevin Hart dropped by Snapchat HQ for a tour and Q&A.

13.title: Rock the Promo - Hosted by Joe Santagato, Feat. Shane "Hurricane" Helms (S1 E4)
13.plot: Joe Santagato and Shane "Hurricane" Helms, have teamed up with The Rock to bring you the forth episode of "Rock The Promo". This week, they'll judge the bottom right bracket of contestants on their humor, intensity, and toughness to see who truly knows how to rock a promo.

14.title: Rio 2016 Olympics: 3 Traditional Sports Banned
14.plot: The Olympics have a history of bizarre events that didn't stand the test of time so Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and his production company, Seven Bucks Digital Studios, reimagine what would happen if actual former events Armored Racing, Painting, and Pistol Dueling were brought back from Olympic retirement.

15.title: Rock the Promo - Hosted by Joe Santagato, Feat. The Rock & Christian (S1 E5)
15.plot: Joe Santagato and Christian have teamed up with The Rock to bring you the fifth episode of "Rock The Promo". This week, they'll judge the 2nd round left bracket of contestants on their humor, intensity, and toughness to see who truly knows how to rock a promo.

16.title: A Personal Message from Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson
16.plot: You wanted a vlog, YouTube? IT DOESN'T MATTER WHAT YOU WANT. The Rock has heard your cries and now he's ready to speak to YOU. Hear what The Rock has to say regarding your favorite YouTube channel and the future that lies ahead.

17.title: Rock the Promo - Hosted by Joe Santagato, Feat. Tommy Dreamer (S1 E6)
17.plot: Joe Santagato and Tommy Dreamer have teamed up with The Rock to bring you the sixth episode of "Rock The Promo". This week, they'll judge the right side bracket of the second round of contestants on their humor, intensity, and toughness to see who truly knows how to rock a promo.

18.title: The Rock Responds to Your Comments! Seven Bucks September Q&A
18.plot: The Rock has been "hiding" in the YouTube comments section as somebody named "DJ" and he's here to react to your burning thoughts, questions, and meanest comments.

19.title: Rock the Promo - Hosted by Joe Santagato, Feat. Cody Rhodes (S1 E7)
19.plot: Joe Santagato and Cody Rhodes have teamed up with The Rock to bring you the 7th episode of "Rock The Promo". This week, they'll judge the Quarterfinal contestants on their humor, intensity, and toughness to see who truly knows how to rock a promo.

20.title: MATAFIED: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson's Signature Style with Robert Mata (E2)
20.plot: Robert Mata, Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson's longtime stylist and wardrobe for Spencer Strasmore on HBO's "Ballers" gives you the inside scoop on how to build a personal, signature style and the secret weapon that ties The Rock's wardrobe together.

21.title: Rock the Promo Tag Team - Hosted by Joe Santagato, Feat. Mick Foley (S1 E8)
21.plot: Joe Santagato and Mick Foley have teamed up with The Rock to bring you the 8th episode of "Rock The Promo". This week, they'll judge the semifinal contestants as they form tag-team duos and will be judged on their humor, intensity, and toughness to see who truly knows how to rock a promo.

22.title: The Rock Is Mr. Olympia's "Man of the Century"!
22.plot: Go behind the scenes as The Rock visits Joe Weider's Olympia Fitness and Performance Weekend with Seven Bucks' own, Dany Garcia. The Rock receives the Olympia's "Man of the Century" Award and honors bobybuilders and weightlifters across the globe.

23.title: Rock the Promo Recap - Not Hosted by Joe Santagato, Feat. Edge (S1 E9)
23.plot: Edge hosts the 9th episode of "Rock The Promo". This week, he'll recap the best moments from the previous 8 episodes, let the losers have the last laugh, and honor Joe Santagato before next week's season finale featuring THE ROCK in Las Vegas.

24.title: Register to Vote in 1:34 with Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson #VoteIRL
24.plot: The Rock and Seven Bucks Digital Studios want you to get out and #voteIRL in this year's elections, so they made you a song.

25.title: Rock the Promo Finale - Hosted by Joe Santagato, Feat. The Rock
25.plot: For the 10th and final episode of "Rock the Promo" we flew the finalists to Las Vegas to perform their promos live in front of Joe Santagato and our legendary guest judge, THE ROCK.

26.title: The Rock Reacts to His First WWE Match: 20 YEARS of the ROCK
26.plot: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson looks back and reacts to some of the great moments of his career.

27.title: FRIDAY NIGHT FRED: Wrestlin' Fred at WWE Monday Night RAW! (E1)
27.plot: Wrestlin' Fred at WWE Monday Night RAW: Welcome to "Friday Night Fred"- the nonsensical pop-culture show hosted by Wrestlin' Fred. Wrestlin' Fred takes to the streets outside WWE's Monday Night RAW to ask the public, what they want to see on his new show.

28.title: and the Rock on the Set of Jumaji
28.plot: We flew some brilliant young adults to Hawaii to jam out in the jungle with The Rock on the set of Jumanji. They're true masters of their musical craft and hungry for greatness. Enjoy a taste of Seven Bucks Productions' "Clash Of The Corps", which gives you unprecedented access to the ultra competitive and amazing world of Drum Corp.

29.title: See What the Rock Has in Store for YouTube! #ROCKTOBER
29.plot: The Rock and the Seven Bucks Digital Studios production team are hard at work on what will be the biggest month for The Rock on YouTube yet. Check out this teaser trailer for what's coming in the next few weeks.

30.title: Seven Bucks' Dany Garcia - The Power of Women
30.plot: Last week the Co-Founder of Seven Bucks Productions, Dany Garcia, was honored at Variety's "Power of Women" event in Los Angeles. We sat down with Dany to discuss what "The Power of Women" means to her and the issues facing women in Hollywood.

31.title: THEROCKSDUBS: The Rock Singing Fifth Harmony's "Work from Home" Feat. Baracksdubs
31.plot: The Rock baracksdubs and join forces for THEROCKSDUBS, a music video of Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson performing Fifth Harmony's "Work From Home.

32.title: The Seance in Room 301
32.plot: As Halloween approaches plenty of spooky surprises lurk around the corner. Watch as some of your favorite YouTubers perform a seance with The Rock in Room 301 and keep your eyeballs open for what's in store next.

33.title: The Rock Answers Questions from YouTubers! Seven Bucks October Q&A
33.plot: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson is back with another Q&A - this time from the set of #JumanjiMovie - and he's here to react to burning questions from some of your favorite YouTubers.

34.title: Escape from Calypso Island
34.plot: To close out #Rocktober, Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and Seven Bucks Productions bring you "Escape From Calypso Island", a 360-degree virtual reality adventure.

35.title: FRIDAY NIGHT FRED: Wrestlin' Fred on the 2016 US Presidential Election (E2)
35.plot: After being summoned by the The People's Champ (AKA The Rock) to go out and, well, uh, speak to the people, Wrestlin' Fred takes to the streets days before the 2016 Presidential Election to ask YOU, THE PEOPLE who you'd want to see in the White House.

36.title: Behind the Scenes of "The Rock Presents: Escape from Calypso Island - A 360 VR Adventure"
36.plot: Go behind the scenes with Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and Seven Bucks Productions as they create "Escape From Calypso Island", a 360-degree virtual reality adventure.

37.title: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson Sets Out to ROCK the TROOPS on Veteran's Day!
37.plot: Just in time for Veteran's Day, Seven Bucks Productions and The Rock are excited to share a preview of "Rock the Troops" - a variety show celebrating our servicemen and women, hosted by The Rock in Hawaii just a few weeks ago. To our veterans, we salute and thank you - there is nothing more rewarding than entertaining you.

38.title: The Rock's "Sexiest Man Alive" Mannequin Challenge
38.plot: In celebration of being named People Magazine's "Sexiest Man Alive", Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and friends give you 2016's sexiest mannequin challenge.

39.title: Unsolicited Advice: Yahoo Answers with the Rock - Seven Bucks November Q&A
39.plot: While on set of the new "Jumanji" film, The Rock is here to provide unsolicited advice in answer to some of the wackiest questions found on Yahoo Answes in the Seven Bucks November Q&A.

40.title: Lin-Manuel Miranda & Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson on the Making of "Millennials: The Musical"
40.plot: Fresh off the heels of their soon-to-be-released Disney movie, #Moana (in theaters Nov. 23rd in 3D), Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and Lin-Manuel Miranda decided to put their producing chops to the test by releasing their very own YouTube musical epic, "Millennials: The Musical".

41.title: Lin-Manuel Miranda & Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson Sing "You're Welcome" (From "Moana")!
41.plot: Live from the red-carpet of #Moana (in theaters NOW in 3D), Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and Lin-Manuel Miranda show off their singing skills with a rendition of song "You're Welcome" from the film.

42.title: Lin-Manuel Miranda and Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson Present "Millennials: The Musical"
42.plot: A loving satire of musical theater and millennial culture. It tells the surprisingly uplifting story of a privileged Brooklynite, Crystal, whose world comes crumbling down when she loses her phone.

43.title: Fun with the Rock, Lin-Manuel Miranda & the Cast of "Millennials: The Musical"!
43.plot: Go behind the scenes with The Rock and Lin-Manuel Miranda as they follow the cast and crew during the production of "Millennials: The Musical".

44.title: Seven Bucks Moment: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson
44.plot: Featuring stories from a variety of guests. Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson: Kicking it off is Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson himself. US Army Veteran Tommy Counihan and his story of overcoming depression through surfing after being wounded in combat in Afghanistan. Sportswriter Jay Glazer reveals the story of his rise to becoming a prominent NFL and MMA journalist. Lilly Singh tells the story of how she overcame depression to become YouTube royalty.

45.title: The Rock's BIG Show!
45.plot: Seven Bucks Productions and The Rock are excited to share an exclusive behind the scenes look of "Rock the Troops" - a variety show celebrating our servicemen and women, hosted by The Rock in Hawaii. Expect more "Rock the Troops" fun here next week. To our veterans, we salute and thank you - there is nothing more rewarding than entertaining you.

46.title: Backstage Pass with the Rock Feat. Kevin Hart, Terry Crews, Tenacious D & More!!
46.plot: Seven Bucks Productions and The Rock are excited to share an exclusive behind the scenes look at "Rock the Troops" - a variety show celebrating our servicemen and women, hosted by The Rock in Hawaii, that premieres tonight on Spike. To our veterans, we salute and thank you - there is nothing more rewarding than entertaining you.

47.title: HOLIDAY LIFT - Working Out with Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson!
47.plot: Even though the holidays are here, Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson never stops working. Join him in the gym as he gets a lift in before the holidays to raise spirits (and his max rep). #MerryRockmas.

48.title: Twas the Night Before Rockmas - Story Time with Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson
48.plot: With the holidays upon us, Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson, aka Dwanta Claus, invites you to gather round for his retelling of a classic Christmas story: "Twas the Night Before Rockmas".

49.title: FRIDAY NIGHT FRED: Cuffing Season Christmas Special with TheZombiUnicorn (E3)
49.plot: As Christmas draws near, Wrestling Fred invites TheZombiUnicorn and Marni Kinrys and Kristen Carney of "Ask Women Podcast" to explore "cuffing season". What's cuffing season?

50.title: ICYMI: The Best of the "Yule Rock" Live Stream
50.plot: #MerryRockmas and Happy Holidays from Seven Bucks Digital Studios. In case you missed it, to celebrate the end of 2016, we did our first ever live stream for 18 hours on Christmas. Here are the highlights from #YuleRock.

51.title: The Rock Thanks You for a Great 2016!
51.plot: 2016 was one helluva year, for the world and for the team here at Seven Bucks Digital Studios. Please enjoy this special "thank you" to the fans from Dwayne 'The Rock' Johnson as he counts down this year's most epic moments. Thanks for being a part of the journey, and here's to a fun-filled 2017.

1.title: The Rock Responds to YouTube Comments - Seven Bucks January Q&A
1.plot: The Rock is ready to start 2017 off with a bang by answering questions from the comments section here on YouTube. We're going to be doing more of these so as always please leave your realest, most pressing questions in the comments.

2.title: Seven Bucks Moment: US Army Veteran Tommy Counihan
2.plot: The 2nd episode of #SevenBucksMoment features US Army veteran Tommy Counihan and his story of overcoming depression through surfing after being wounded in combat in Afghanistan.

3.title: The Rock's Big Summer Movie
3.plot: On May 26, 2017, Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and a few of his friends are hitting the beach to save some lives and have a little fun along the way.

4.title: Tom Brady Takes on the Rock
4.plot: New England Patriots quarterback Tom Brady has won 4 Super Bowls and has been named NFL MVP twice, but he made a mistake when he decided to call out Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson in a new video message.

5.title: Welcome to Seven Bucks Digital Studios!
5.plot: After launching this channel in 2016, Seven Bucks Digital Studios and The Rock are ready to break YouTube with an EPIC 2017. We have to thank you, the fans, for making this a reality.

6.title: The Rock Surprises a US Army Combat Veteran with a 2018 Ford Mustang!
6.plot: When Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson visited Ford's design studio in Detroit last month, he was so inspired by what he saw that he and the Ford Motor Company decided to surprise a US Army combat veteran named Marlene with the all-new 2018 Ford Mustang. Thank you Ford for helping Dwayne, Seven Bucks, and Marlene.

7.title: Smash the Like, Save a Puppy
7.plot: Smash that like to save some french bulldog puppies. The Rock and Seven Bucks Digital Studios will donate the first 90 days of ad revenue from this video to the Best Friends Animal Society.

8.title: January Lift - Kindness with Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson
8.plot: In the 2nd installment of our monthly LIFT series we hope to lift something besides heavy weights - your spirits. Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson reminds us of the importance of being kind to those around you.

9.title: Crazy Uber Ride with Masked Driver: 100 Tacos & Pauly Shore
9.plot: Wrestlin' Fred, afraid that The Rock hasn't called him in months, conducts a social experiment to get Dwayne's attention.

10.title: -30 Degree Wind Tunnel at the Ford Factory!
10.plot: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson spent three days at the Ford factory in Detroit shooting some commercials, including some scenes in Ford's -30 degree wind tunnel.

11.title: We Broke a Guinness World Record!
11.plot: In preparation for the Super Bowl, the Rock's Seven Bucks Digital Studio squad sets out to break a Guinness World Record by building the BIGGEST, BADDEST bean dip in town.

12.title: The Rock & Rob Gronkowski Go Crazy After the Patriots Win the Super Bowl
12.plot: The Rock and New England Patriots legend Rob Gronkowski celebrate Super Bowl LI by celebrating football and #Baywatch.

13.title: Seven Bucks Moment: Sportswriter Jay Glazer
13.plot: Jay Glazer reveals the story of his rise to becoming a prominent NFL and MMA journalist.

14.title: Zac Efron and Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson: Valentine's Day BFFs!
14.plot: For Valentine's Day, Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and Zac Efron take a look back at all their wild and manly adventures together. Turns out, filming #Baywatch was just the tip of the iceberg for these two.

15.title: The Rock's Black Adam: A Hero? - Seven Bucks February Q&A
15.plot: You have questions and Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson has answers in the February Q&A.

16.title: The Rock's New HBO Documentary: "Rock and a Hard Place" (Trailer)
16.plot: On March 27, HBO will air The Rock's new documentary "Rock And A Hard Place", inspired by his own experience with the law as a youth.

17.title: February Lift - The Rock on Set of "The Fate of the Furious"!
17.plot: Watch the coolest moments from Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson's time filming "The Fate Of The Furious", out April 14, 2017.

18.title: Logan Paul Has Been Cut from, Like, All of the Rock's Movies
18.plot: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson calls a face-to-face meeting with Logan Paul to deliver some disappointing news.

19.title: What Really Happened with the 2017 Oscars Best Picture Mistake (According to the Rock)
19.plot: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson was in the house to witness the wild 2017 Oscars Best Picture mistake with "La La Land" and "Moonlight".

20.title: The Rock's Ultimate Workout
20.plot: A look into The Rock's workout. See what it takes to be the sexiest man alive.

21.title: ACTION SCIENCE: Hobbs (The Rock) vs. Shaw (Jason Statham) in "Furious 7"
21.plot: "Action Science" breaks down the science of the most epic movie fight scenes with Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson.

22.title: The Truth About Wrestling - Seven Bucks March Q&A
22.plot: You have questions and Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson has answers in his latest Q&A.

23.title: Matafield: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson's Style on a Budget with Robert Mata (E3)
23.plot: Robert Mata, Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson's longtime stylist and costume designer on HBO's "Ballers" gives you the inside scoop on how to build a personal, signature style and the secret weapon that will allow you to be a baller on a budget.

24.title: Don't Steal Cookies: The Rock's HBO Documentary "Rock and a Hard Place"
24.plot: On March 27, HBO will air The Rock's new documentary "Rock And A Hard Place". Watch an exclusive clip now.

25.title: Seven Bucks Moment: Lilly Singh (Superwoman)
25.plot: YouTube superstar Lilly Singh (AKA IISuperwomanII) tells the story of how she overcame depression to become YouTube royalty.

26.title: Heavy Lift - Goofs, Gaffs, & Laughs with Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson
26.plot: Ahead of April Fool's, watch The Rock joke with friends and family.

27.title: The Rock Reacts to His First Leading Role in "The Scorpion King": 15 Years Later
27.plot: For the 15th Anniversary of the release of "The Scorpion King", The Rock reflects on his first leading role. Dwayne tells us what really went down on set.

28.title: The Rock's EXCLUSIVE First Look at "The Fate of the Furious"
28.plot: Check out this EXCLUSIVE clip of Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson talking about his character, Luke Hobbs, in the 8th installment of "The Fast and the Furious" series, "The Fate of the Furious" in theaters April 14th.

29.title: The Rock, Zac Efron, and Priyanka Chopra Presents the "Baywatch" Trailer at Cinemacon
29.plot: Join Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and the cast of "Baywatch" ( Zac Efron, Priyanka Chopra, Alexandra Daddario) as they hang with stars like George Clooney and Al Gore at CinemaCon 2017.

30.title: The Rock's Love Advice - Seven Bucks April Q&A
30.plot: You have questions and Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson has singing, genie jokes, theories about a Rob Gronkowski hybrid, and answers in his latest Q&A.

31.title: Logan Paul Is, Like, Totally Terrible at Falling in Love with Alexandra Daddario
31.plot: While trying to impress The Rock so that he could earn a spot on the Baywatch team, Logan Paul falls head over heels for Alexandra Daddario and fights to gain her love #baewatch.

32.title: The Rock Thanks You for 2 Million Subscribers!
32.plot: It's been a FAST and FURIOUS ride ever since The Rock's channel launched 9 months ago, but thanks to viewers like you, we have hit the 2 million subscriber mark.

33.title: The Rock Takes Over New York City During "The Fate of the Furious" Premiere
33.plot: Come take a fast and furious ride along with Dwayne on the red carpet of "The Fate of the Furious" premiere in NYC.

34.title: The Rock's Birthday Surprise!
34.plot: The Rock's friends, Jimmy Fallon, Kevin Hart, Lilly Singh (Superwoman), Jack Black, Karen Gillan and MORE wish Dwayne a happy 45th birthday. You give us so much every day and we want to give you something back. Thank you for being the best boss, creator, and role model.

35.title: The Rock Basically Slows Down Time
35.plot: Check out The Rock's BFF Nick Mundy crash the red carpet for "Baywatch" and commentate the first ever SlowMo Marathon in Downtown L.A.

36.title: Action Science: The Rock vs. An Entire Army in "The Rundown"
36.plot: Get "The Rundown" of how the Rock defies physics.

37.title: Baller's Lift: The Rock's Most Ballin' Moments from the Set
37.plot: Ahead of the season 3 premiere of HBO's "Ballers", watch The Rock greeting fans on the set and being a straight up baller.

38.title: The Rock and Logan Paul's "THE SONG of the SUMMER" Ft. Desiigner (Official Music Video)
38.plot: The ultimate summer 2017 song that features music by Desiigner, and a special appearance by the one and only David Hasselhoff.

39.title: The Rock Reacts to His Favorite Sketches from Saturday Night Live: Part 1
39.plot: On the eve of Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson's 5th time hosting SNL, we look back and reflect on some of his favorite sketches.

40.title: Logan Paul, Like, Finally Gets a Call from Alexandra Daddario
40.plot: As our summer saga comes to a close, Alexandra Daddario phones up Logan to discuss the possibilities of a budding romance. This Video also includes a behind the scenes look at what it took to make the song of the summer.

41.title: The Rock Reacts to His Favorite Sketches from Saturday Night Live: Part 2
41.plot: On the eve of Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson's 5th time hosting SNL, we look back and reflect on some of even more of his favorite sketches.

42.title: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson's Miami Beach Takeover
42.plot: Join Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and the cast of Baywatch as they take over Miami, Florida for the world premiere.

43.title: Logan Paul's "THE SONG of the SUMMER" (Party Edit) Ft. Desiigner
43.plot: Check out The Rock and Logan Paul's #SongOfTheSummer.

44.title: June Lift: The Rock Shows Us How to Hip Thrust!
44.plot: Revisit the The Rock's favorite moments from the past month of his life. SUBSCRIBE for more.

45.title: The Rock Makes Grown Men Cry - Seven Bucks June Q&A
45.plot: You have questions and Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson has answers in his latest Q&A. Leave your questions in the comments below for the next Q&A.

46.title: Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson's Super Fan Goes Too Far!
46.plot: Nick Mundy has been stealing cutouts of the Rock for years, and it's up to Jon Bass and Adam Lustick to take him down.

47.title: The Rock and Seven Bucks Digital Studios - For Your Consideration
47.plot: The Rock and Seven Bucks are back, except this time, they're trying to win the coveted Emmy for outstanding digital short form variety series.

48.title: Bro/Science/Life - The Series - The Trailer
48.plot: Seven Bucks Digital Studios and Studio71 have teamed up with BroScienceLife (Dom Mazzetti) to bring you a new series of epic proportions coming to June 30th and the weeks to follow.

49.title: The Rock Tag Teams with Dom Mazzetti! Bro/Science/Life: The Series (E1)
49.plot: Go ahead, skip leg day and watch this a million times on repeat. Seven Bucks Digital Studios has teamed up with BroScienceLife to bring you a new series following Dom Mazzetti on his journey as he attempts to open up his own gym, The Church of Iron.

50.title: The Rock's Independence Day Backyard Brawl with Wonder Woman's Samantha Jo
50.plot: When the 4th of July gets too hot to handle, it's time to call...The Designated Driver. Get ready for a fight on the 4th, starring renowned martial artist and stunt woman Samantha Jo.

51.title: The Rock Presents Dom Mazzetti's Training Program! Bro/Science/Life (E2)
51.plot: Go ahead, skip leg day and watch this a million times on repeat. Seven Bucks Digital Studios has teamed up with Bro Science Life to bring you a new series following Dom Mazzetti on his journey as he attempts to open up his own gym, The Church of Iron.

52.title: Get Pumped Up for "Ballers" Season 3 with the Rock
52.plot: In preparation for the launch of season three of "Ballers" on 7/23, Dwayne gets you up to speed with anything that you may have missed.

53.title: The End of Dom Mazzetti? Bro/Science/Life: The Series (Episode 3)
53.plot: Get back on the Smith Machine, haters. It's time for the third episode of Bro/Science/Life The Series.

54.title: ACTION SCIENCE: The Rock vs. A Tsunami in "San Andreas"
54.plot: Raymond Gaines (The Rock) is in a speedboat race for his life as he pushes the limits of physics in this episode of Action Science.

55.title: Dom Mazzetti's Secrets of the "Swoly Bible" with the Cast of Bro/Science/Life
55.plot: How did Dom save his gym? The cast of Bro/Science/Life share the truth inside the Church of Iron.

56.title: The Rock's State of the YouTube Address
56.plot: After one year on YouTube, The Rock address his fans and discusses the future of the channel.

57.title: The Rock's Favorite Moments from HBO's "Ballers"
57.plot: Get ready for "Ballers" Season 3 with the Rock's favorite scenes.

imdb.title: Seven Bucks Digital Studios
plot: The official YouTube channel for Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and _Seven Bucks Digital Studios_ (qv). New videos every Tuesday.
